{"tid":2222174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒙古前總統去信習近平　抗議推普滅蒙教材　駐蒙大使館：觀點完全錯誤","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T04:16:24.000Z","uid":261647,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"164c211c07b43490bdd1e1bf04c72566d553721a","tid":2222174,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3497200467032215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3497200467032215&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=8e1ecb06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3497200467032215</a><br />\n<br />\n內蒙古教育部門早前要求所有學校用漢語取代蒙古語教學，引發當地民眾示威。蒙古國前總統額勒貝格道爾吉（Elbegdorj Tsakhia）昨日（25 日）去信中國國家主席習近平，抗議中國在內蒙古強推漢語教材。額勒貝格道爾吉今日在 Twitter 稱，信件已被中國駐蒙古大使館退回。他亦強調，不會收回該封信件，指有關信件已引起越來越多人關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkzUzBO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkzUzBO.png&h=5e44931e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《香港電台》引述中國駐蒙古大使柴文睿致函額勒貝格道爾吉的信件，表示包括內蒙雙語教育改革在內的一切涉內蒙古事務，都是中國內政，不容他人干涉，指對方日前致函中國領導人的信函，所闡述的觀點完全錯誤，中方不予接受，希望他以兩國關係大局出發，尊重中國主權，認清事實真相，秉持正確立場，停止炒作有關問題。"},{"pid":"3dff87d7fd5760353c1f984eabef1a2d01b6071b","tid":2222174,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JBGX26nNLlwLl9q7t1v15A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/a731725074d62123c3bd2cb8d211eddf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJBGX26nNLlwLl9q7t1v15A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fa731725074d62123c3bd2cb8d211eddf&h=0fa89b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/%E6%96%87cover-8-990x520.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E6%2596%2587cover-8-990x520.png&h=ebb17b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/27/197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F197.jpg&h=09f146bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99373fa5ea4b898d875b748bd171f49c435eff0b","tid":2222174,"uid":77164,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"中國做外交官真係方便"},{"pid":"1b452c91c6d1508304769b4556849a665e8156b5","tid":2222174,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"唔通話你屌得啱咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔認錯嘅獨裁政權"},{"pid":"4f4adbf21cb90e9fbbe5abd8b20a4641d85ac640","tid":2222174,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a80b0ed45fa542c4701f32c6b6c3e2a93a1539","tid":2222174,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"維尼：好驚MQ-9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33c65d0197070d3003624d74cdb0e4d1de4e21f","tid":2222174,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"又干預內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，責任全在蒙方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51fb11d470025407423881152df94bbd0647fc9","tid":2222174,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202